description: [``botocore``] Added DryRun parameter to CreateEnvironmentEC2 API. Added ManagedCredentialsActions parameter to UpdateEnvironment API
[``botocore``] This release adds support for EC2 ED25519 key pairs for authentication
[``botocore``] This release is a new feature for Cost Categories: Split charge rules. Split charge rules enable you to allocate shared costs between your cost category values.
